== Reception ==
The review by [[AllMusic]] critique Dave Lynch awarded the album 4.5 stars.<ref name=allmusic>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/grand-general-mw0002480363 |title=Ola Kvernberg - Grand General |work=Musical review |first=Dave |last=Lynch |publisher=[[AllMusic]] |year=2013 |accessdate=2014-05-03}}</ref>

