== Musicians ==
*[[Ola Kvernberg]] - violins & viola 
*[[Even Helte Hermansen]] - guitar
*[[Erlend Slettevoll]] - keyboards
*[[Trond Frønes]] - bass
*[[Kenneth Kapstad]] - drums

